    <!-- Schedule Section -->
    <div class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Schedule</h2>
      <p class="mt-4">
        The detailed event schedule will be emailed to attendeess. In general, programming will follow some form of this outline:
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        Day 1 - Friday, February 21: 10 AM - 4 PM
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4">
        <li>Welcome Remarks and Hashrate Heating Overview for Novices</li>
        <li>Heat Reuse Potential & Target Market- Why do this? Economic feasibility. Who's best fit for this? How big is the market?</li>
        <li>Business Model Roundtable. What kinds of business are possible with hashrate heating? How does this change product and service offerings in the heating industry?</li>
        <li>Product Demos & Hands on with Hashrate Heating Hardware.</li>
        <li>Small Scale Mining. 120 V Loki Rigs, Bitaxes, and the importance of plug-and-play simple home mining solutions.</li>
        <li>Adoption Landscape - What does it take to change the status quo of bitcoin mining? How does this scale to the average person? What are the regulatory hurdles?</li>
        <li>Heatpunk's Manifesto - What do we believe and what is our mission? How will we promote prosperity while reamining true to the bitcoin network?</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">
        Day 2 - Saturday, February 22: 9 AM - 3:30 PM
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4">
        <li>Controlling Hashrate Heaters - Home mining control and management - from space heaters to integrated heating systems.</li>
        <li>Delivery Systems Debate - Air vs Immersion vs Hydro for heat reuse. What integrates best into heating systems?</li>
        <li>Firmware, Software and Pools - What role do code and software features play in home mining and heating infrastructure?</li>
        <li>Product Demos & Hands on with Hashrate Heating Hardware.</li>
        <li>Bitmain or Bust? - Are we bound by Bitmain and MicroBT? What does the future of ASIC options mean for home mining and heating devices?</li>
        <li>Challenges Ahead and Contractor Feedback - What challenges do we need to go overcome? Call to action. HVAC, Hydronic Plumbing, Electrical and other expert input. What miners need to know.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Attendees Section -->
    <div class="mt-10">
