        <li>Hashrate Heating Designers: Nakamoto Heating Solutions, Unbound Networks, Anadro, Softwarm LLC, 256Heat, Exergy LLC, HBIM, Untethered Mining, Constellation Heating, Hashrate House, Warm Bitcoin, Mint Green</li>
